der to document any&nbsp; telephone conversations that we may have in the future.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.5249977111816406pt;margin-right: 13.62371826171875pt;text-indent: 0.483001708984375pt;margin-top:10.875762939453125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Furthermore, if any negative information is placed on my credit bureau reports by your agency after receipt of this&nbsp; notice, this will cause me to file suit against you and your organization, both personally and corporately, to seek any&nbsp; and all legal remedies available to me by law.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.5564994812011719pt;margin-right: 4.71142578125pt;text-indent: 0.5670013427734375pt;margin-top:10.875762939453125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">It is my policy neither to recognize nor deal with collection agencies, and I will only settle this account with the original&nbsp; creditor.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.6194992065429688pt;margin-top:10.875762939453125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Sincerely,&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4409980773925781pt;margin-top:10.996505737304688pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Aria