t-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">I understand the debt is due, however your repeated attempts to collect are causing me much stress and therefore I&nbsp; must also ask you to cease and desist you (if the account is being pursued by a third party debt collector). If my&nbsp; situation changes, I will contact you immediately.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.9134979248046875pt;margin-top:10.875747680664062pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Kind regards,&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4409980773925781pt;margin-top:10.996505737304688pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">{client_signature}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:10.996505737304688pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">_________________________________________&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span id="docs-internal-guid-05585267-7fff-e62c-9827-f01507fc4521"></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4409980773925781pt;margin-top:10.996505737304688pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">{client_first_name} {client_last_name} </span></p>');


