-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Specifically you: [list all that apply]&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4829978942871094pt;margin-top:10.996490478515625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">- Failed to validate a debt at my request- FDCPA violation&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4829978942871094pt;margin-top:10.996490478515625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">- Continued to report a disputed debt to the CRA- FCRA violation&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4829978942871094pt;margin-top:10.996490478515625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">- Continued to attempt to collect a disputed debt- FDCPA violation&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4829978942871094pt;margin-top:10.996490478515625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">- Ignored my cease and desist- FDCPA violation&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>