nt;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">I am aware of the funds due to you and of the judgment placed against me for those funds. I had every intention of&nbsp; taking care of this prior to the entry of the judgment, but unfortunately time constraints made that impossible for me.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.3885002136230469pt;margin-right: 24.33892822265625pt;text-indent: -0.4305000305175781pt;margin-top:10.875762939453125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0.4305000305175781pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Today, I am writing to you in the hope that we may put this matter behind us and settle out the judgment for good,&nbsp; under a few conditions. This will save you both time and money trying to collect the judgment and will help me to&nbsp; recover from your negative entry in my credit history reports.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.5249977111816406pt;margin-right: 14.63067626953125pt;text-indent: 0.5985031127929688pt;margin-top:10.875762939453125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">I have been offered a loan from a close family member to pay you (amount you are offering) to settle the debt in-full&nbsp; and have the judgment dismissed.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.05249786376953125pt;margin-right: 14.4664306640625pt;text-indent: -0.09450149536132812pt;margin-top