e;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Social security number&nbsp;</span></p>',5,1,'2020-10-20 23:47:39','2020-10-21 23:24:33',1),(60,'Pay For Delete (Alternate 3)','<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4409980773925781pt;margin-top:5.8304443359375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">{client_first_name} {client_last_name}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4409980773925781pt;margin-top:10.99652099609375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">{client_address}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4409980773925781pt;margin-top:34.24652099609375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">{creditor_name}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.7244987487792969pt;margin-top:34.24652099609375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&lt;CREDITOR/FURNISHER ADDRESS&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.9554977416992188pt;margin-top:34.24652099609375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Dear Collection Manager:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.6300010681152344pt;margin-right: 5.67169189453125pt;text-indent: 0.493499755859375pt;margin-top:10.99652099609375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">It has come to my attention through the credit bureaus that you claim I owe a debt to your agency. While I have never&nbsp; had the debt verified to me as legitimate by your agency, I may be willing to save us both some time and effort by&nbsp; \"settling the debt out\" with restrictions.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.819000244140625pt;margin-right: 3.682861328125pt;text-indent: 0.3045005798339844pt;margin-top:10.875732421875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">I understand that you hold all the rights to report the debt to the credit bureaus as you see fit and you can change that&nbsp; listing at any time, as the source owning the debt. I am sure you are aware of my right to dispute this debt and to&nbsp; request full proof of the obligation as per the FDCPA. Paying this unverified debt means little to me if we cannot&nbsp; mutually agree that you will report the debt as mentioned below.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.2729988098144531pt;margin-right: 6.08880615234375pt;text-indent: -0.546001434