 about my financial ability. I will&nbsp; pay your company the amount of $(AMOUNT) as \"payment in full\" for this account. Upon receipt of the above&nbsp; payment, your company has agreed to delete the item on my credit reports.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.17850112915039062pt;margin-right: 0.02374267578125pt;text-indent: 0.9449996948242188pt;margin-top:10.875762939453125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">If you agree with these terms please acknowledge this letter with your signature and return it to me. You agree that the&nbsp; terms herein are confidential and that you have the authority to make such decisions. No payment will be made&nbsp; without written confirmation from you.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2138000011444092;margin-left: 0.5249977111816406pt;margin-right: 1.22149658203125pt;text-indent: 0.45149993896484375pt;margin-top:10.875762939453125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Upon receipt of this signed acknowledgment, I will immediately mail you a cashier\'s check by priority mail. This is not&nbsp; a renewed promise to pay but rather a restricted offer only. If no terms can be met, no new arrangements will be made&nbsp; and the offer will be void.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:34.12574768066406pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;verti